## Part B — Permissions onboarding (apps/mobile/lib/screens/onboarding/)

### PermissionsOnboardingScreen
- Shown once at first launch. Check on app start: if `SharedPreferences.getBool('onboarding_complete') != true`, redirect to this screen before the dashboard.
- Two sequential steps rendered as a PageView:

**Step 1 — When In Use**
- Icon: map pin
- Headline: "Show your location on the map"
- Body: "We use your location to center the map when you set a reminder spot."
- Button: "Continue" → calls `permission_handler`'s `Permission.locationWhenInUse.request()`
- If denied: show inline note "You can set locations manually by tapping the map" and allow proceeding

**Step 2 — Always On**
